long_description: The women's Timex Ironman 10-lap watch offers indispensable, Ironman-ready features for athletes at any level. This watch features 10-lap memory recall and a 24-hr. countdown timer with stop and repeat capabilities. Daily, weekday and weekend alarms with 5 min. backup help keep you on schedule. Time, month, day and date are displayed with large, easy-to-read digits. INDIGLO(R) Night-Light with Night-Mode activates lighting with the push of a button. Resin strap and case provide comfort and durability. The Timex Ironman 10-lap watch is water resistant to 100m (330 ft).
